description: PA/23/00952 - Tower Hamlets: Request for an Environmental Impact Assessment (EIA) Scoping Opinion under Regulation 15 of the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 2017 (as amended), in respect of a Proposed Development comprising the demolition of the existing structures on site and the construction of a new tower building of up to 38 storeys for the provision of up to 360 residential units (Class C3), 600m2 flexible community / commercial floorspace and associated works.
